A 360 degree video player written in AS3 using the Papervision 3D library.
The code also allows for a second video to be played at the bottom of the sphere.

The final product was used on Doritos Late Night:
http://doritoslatenight.com

The included video sample is from our test shoot using a LadyBug camera:
http://www.ptgrey.com/index.asp

Papervision3D:
http://papervision3d.org/
http://code.google.com/p/papervision3d/downloads/list

Also uses TweenLite class:
https://greensock.com/tweenlite/